{
  "id": "common.virgins.virg2",
  "kind": "common",
  "scope": "universal",
  "structure": "mass",
  "title": {
    "la": "COMMUNE VIRGINUM II. PRO UNA VIRGINE 2",
    "es": "COMÚN DE VÍRGENES II. Para una virgen 2",
    "en-US": "Common of Virgins Ii. For One Virgin 2",
    "pt-BR": "Comum das virgens 2",
    "it": "COMUNE DELLE VERGINI II. PRO UNA VIRGINE 2",
    "fr": "COMMUN DES VIERGES II. POUR UNE VIERGE 2",
    "de": "COMMUNE-TEXTE FÜR JUNGFRAUEN 2."
  },
  "color": "white",
  "rank": "weekday",
  "cycleScheme": "fixed",
  "includeGloria": false,
  "entranceAntiphon": {
    "options": [
      {
        "body": {
          "lines": {
            "la": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Hæc est virgo sápiens, quam Dóminus vigilántem invénit, quæ accéptis lampádibus sumpsit secum óleum et, veniénte Dómino, introívit cum eo ad núptias"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "T. P."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "allelúia"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "es": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Esta es la virgen sabia que el Señor encontró vigilante, con el aceite de su lámpara preparado y, al llegar el Señor, entró con él en el banquete de bodas"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "T. P."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Aleluya"
                }
              ]
            ],
            "en-US": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Here is a wise virgin whom the Lord found watching; when they took up their lamps she brought oil with her and when the Lord came she went in with him to the wedding feast"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "E. T."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "alleluia"
                }
              ]
            ],
            "it": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Esta es la virgen sabia que el Señor encontró vigilante, con el aceite de su lámpara preparado y, al llegar el Señor, entró con él en el banquete de bodas"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "T. P."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Alleluia"
                }
              ]
            ],
            "fr": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Que tu es belle, vierge du Christ !"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Tu as mérité de recevoir la couronne du Seigneur,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "la couronne de la virginité à jamais"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "T. P."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "alléluia"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "."
                }
              ]
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "collect": {
    "options": [
      {
        "body": {
          "lines": {
            "la": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Fac, Dómine Deus noster, ut beáta virgo"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", sponsa tibi fidélis, divínæ caritátis flammam éxcitet in córdibus nostris, quam, ad perénnem Ecclésiæ tuæ glóriam, áliis virgínibus inséruit. Per Dóminum."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "es": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Señor, Dios nuestro,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "haz que santa"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", virgen,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "tu fiel esposa,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "avive en nuestros corazones la llama del mismo amor divino que encendió en otras vírgenes,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "para gloria perpetua de tu Iglesia."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Por nuestro Señor Jesucristo."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "en-US": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Grant, O Lord our God, that the Virgin blessed"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ","
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "your faithful spouse, may stir up in our hearts the flame of divine love,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "which she inspired in other virgins to the enduring glory of your Church."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Through our Lord Jesus Christ, your Son,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "who lives and reigns with you in the unity of the Holy Spirit,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "one God, for ever and ever."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "pt-BR": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Senhor nosso Deus, que a santa virgem"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", vossa fiel esposa, desperte em nosso coração a chama da caridade, que ela transmitiu a outras virgens para a glória perene de vossa Igreja. Por nosso Senhor Jesus Cristo, vosso Filho, na unidade do Espírito Santo."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "it": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Donaci, Signore Dio nostro, la fiamma di carità che la santa vergine"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", sposa a te fedele, fece ardere nel cuore delle sue sorelle a gloria perenne della tua Chiesa. Per il nostro Signore Gesù Cristo, tuo Figlio, che è Dio, e vive e regna con te, nell’unità dello Spirito Santo, per tutti i secoli dei secoli."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "fr": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Seigneur notre Dieu,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "fais que la vierge sainte"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", ton épouse fidèle,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "attise en nos cœurs ce foyer d’amour qu’elle fit brûler dans l’âme de ses compagnes,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "pour la gloire éternelle de ton Église."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Par Jésus Christ, ton Fils, notre Seigneur,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "qui vit et règne avec toi dans l’unité du Saint-Esprit,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Dieu, pour les siècles des siècles."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "de": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Herr, unser Gott, du hast die heilige Jungfrau"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "zu deiner getreuen Braut erwählt. Entflamme auch in unseren Herzen das Feuer der göttlichen Liebe, das sie ihren Gefährtinnen weitergegeben hat zum Ruhm deiner Kirche. Darum bitten wir durch Jesus Christus."
                }
              ]
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "prayerOverOfferings": {
    "options": [
      {
        "body": {
          "lines": {
            "la": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Dicátæ, quǽsumus, Dómine, capiámus oblatiónis efféctum, ut, beátæ"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "exémplo, terrénæ vetustátis conversatióne mundáti,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "cæléstis vitæ proféctibus innovémur. Per Christum."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "es": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Señor, concédenos recibir el fruto de estas ofrendas que te presentamos,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "para que, a ejemplo de santa"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ","
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "limpios de la antigua condición pecadora,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "nos renovemos con la prenda de la vida celestial."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Por Jesucristo, nuestro Señor."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "en-US": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "May we receive, O Lord, we pray, the effects of this offering dedicated to you, so that we may be cleansed from old earthly ways and, through the example of blessed"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", be renewed by growth in heavenly life."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Through Christ our Lord."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "pt-BR": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Fazei-nos, ó Pai, alcançar os frutos dos dons que vos consagramos, e, a exemplo de santa"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", sejamos purificados de todo o mal, e orientados para uma vida nova. Por Cristo, nosso Senhor."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "it": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "L’offerta di questo sacrificio, o Signore, ci liberi dall’antica schiavitù del peccato, perché, sull’esempio di santa"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", possiamo camminare in novità di vita. Per Cristo nostro Signore."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "fr": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Nous proclamons tes merveilles,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "accomplies en la bienheureuse vierge, sainte"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ","
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Seigneur, Dieu de majesté,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "et nous te supplions humblement :"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "toi qui appréciais les mérites de sa vie,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "accepte l’hommage de notre service."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Par le Christ, notre Seigneur."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "de": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Herr, unser Gott, nimmt die Gaben an, die wir darbringen, und mache das heilige Opfer in uns wirksam. Befreie uns, gleich der heiligen"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", von der alten Anhänglichkeit an das Böse und lass das neue Leben der Gnade in uns wachsen. Darum bitten wir durch Christus,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "unseren Herrn."
                }
              ]
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "prefaces": [
    {
      "id": "pf057",
      "label": {
        "la": "PRÆFATIO DE SANCTIS VIRGINIBUS ET RELIGIOSIS",
        "es": "PREFACIO DE SANTAS VÍRGENES Y RELIGIOSOS",
        "en-US": "Preface of Holy Virgins and Religious",
        "pt-BR": "Prefácio das Santas Virgens e Religiosos o",
        "it": "PREFAZIO DELLE SANTE VERGINI E DEI SANTI RELIGIOSI",
        "fr": "PRÉFACE DES SAINTES VIERGES, ET DES SAINTS RELIGIEUX OU RELIGIEUSES",
        "de": "PRÄFATION VON DEN HEILIGEN JUNGFRAUEN UND ORDENSLEUTEN"
      },
      "excerpt": {
        "la": "De signo vitæ Deo consecratæ",
        "es": "Significado de la vida de consagración exclusiva a Dios",
        "en-US": "The sign of a life consecrated to God",
        "pt-BR": "sinal da vida consagrada a Deus",
        "it": "Il segno della vita consacrata a Dio",
        "fr": "Signification de la vie consacrée",
        "de": "Die Zeichenhaftigkeit des gottgeweihten Lebens"
      },
      "body": {
        "lines": {
          "la": [
            [
              {
                "type": "rubric",
                "text": "Sequens præfatio dicitur in sollemnitatibus et festis Sanctarum Virginum et Sanctorum Religiosorum. Dici potest in memoriis ipsorum."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Vere dignum et iustum est,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "æquum et salutáre,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "nos tibi semper et ubíque grátias ágere:"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Dómine, sancte Pater, omnípotens ætérne Deus:"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "In Sanctis enim, qui Christo se dedicavérunt propter regnum cælórum,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "tuam decet providéntiam celebráre mirábilem,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "qua humánam substántiam et ad primæ oríginis révocas sanctitátem,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "et perdúcis ad experiénda dona,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "quæ in novo sǽculo sunt habénda."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Et ídeo, cum Sanctis et Angelis univérsis,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "te collaudámus, sine fine dicéntes:"
              }
            ]
          ],
          "es": [
            [
              {
                "type": "rubric",
                "text": "El siguiente prefacio se dice en las solemnidades y fiestas de las santas Vírgenes y de los santos Religiosos. Se puede decir también en las memorias de los mismos."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "En verdad es justo y necesario,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "es nuestro deber y salvación darte gracias siempre y en todo lugar, Señor, Padre santo,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Dios todopoderoso y eterno."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Porque celebramos tu providencia admirable en los santos que se entregaron a Cristo por el reino de los cielos."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Por ella llamas de nuevo a la humanidad a la santidad primera que de ti había recibido,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "y la conduces a gustar los dones que espera recibir en el cielo."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Por eso,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "con los santos y todos los ángeles,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "te alabamos, proclamando sin cesar:"
              }
            ]
          ],
          "en-US": [
            [
              {
                "type": "rubric",
                "text": "The following Preface is said on the Solemnities and Feasts of Holy Virgins and Religious. It may also be said on their Memorials."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "It is truly right and just, our duty and our salvation,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "always and everywhere to give you thanks,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Lord, holy Father, almighty and eternal God."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "For in the Saints who consecrated themselves to Christ for the sake of the Kingdom of Heaven,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "it is right to celebrate the wonders of your providence,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "by which you call human nature back to its original holiness and bring it to experience on this earth the gifts you promise in the new world to come."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "And so, with all the Angels and Saints,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "we praise you, as without end we acclaim:"
              }
            ]
          ],
          "pt-BR": [
            [
              {
                "type": "rubric",
                "text": "Este prefácio deve ser usado nas solenidades e festas das Santas Virgens e dos Santos Religiosos; ele pode ser rezado também em suas memórias."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Na verdade, é digno e justo,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "é nosso dever e salvação dar-vos graças,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "sempre e em todo lugar,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Senhor, Pai santo,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Deus eterno e todo-poderoso."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Recordando os Santos e Santas que se consagraram a Cristo por amor ao reino dos céus,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "celebramos a vossa admirável providência;"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "por ela, reconduzis a humanidade à santidade original e nos fazeis saborear, já aqui na terra,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "os dons reservados para o céu."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Por isso, com todos os Anjos e Santos,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "nós vos louvamos,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "cantando"
              },
              {
                "type": "rubric",
                "text": "("
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "dizendo"
              },
              {
                "type": "rubric",
                "text": ")"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "a uma só voz:"
              }
            ]
          ],
          "it": [
            [
              {
                "type": "rubric",
                "text": "Si dice nelle solennità e nelle feste delle sante vergini e dei santi religiosi. Si può dire anche nelle loro memorie."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "È veramente cosa buona e giusta,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "renderti grazie e innalzare a te l’inno di benedizione e di lode,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Dio onnipotente ed eterno."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Nei tuoi santi, che per il regno dei cieli hanno consacrato la vita a Cristo tuo Figlio,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "noi celebriamo, o Padre,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "l’iniziativa mirabile del tuo amore,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "poiché tu riporti l’uomo alla santità della sua prima origine e gli fai pregustare i doni che a lui prepari nel mondo rinnovato."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Per questo segno della tua bontà,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "uniti agli angeli e ai santi,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "con voce unanime cantiamo l’inno della tua gloria:"
              }
            ]
          ],
          "fr": [
            [
              {
                "type": "rubric",
                "text": "Cette Préface se dit pendant les solennités et les fêtes des saintes vierges et des saints religieux ou religieuses. On peut aussi l’utiliser dans le cas d’une mémoire liturgique."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Vraiment, il est juste et bon,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "pour ta gloire et notre salut,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "de t’offrir notre action de grâce,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "toujours et en tout lieu,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Seigneur, Père très saint,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Dieu éternel et tout-puissant."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Nous célébrons les prévenances de ton amour pour tant d’hommes et de femmes parvenus à la sainteté en se donnant au Christ à cause du royaume des Cieux."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Par ce mystère d’alliance,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "tu veux que notre condition humaine retrouve sa splendeur première,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "et que, dès ici-bas, nous ayons un avant-goût des biens que tu nous donneras dans le monde à venir."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "C’est pourquoi, avec les saints et tous les anges,"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "nous te louons et sans fin nous proclamons :"
              }
            ]
          ],
          "de": [
            [
              {
                "type": "rubric",
                "text": "Diese Präfation wird an Hochfesten und Festen von Jungfrauen und Ordensleuten genommen."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "In Wahrheit ist es würdig und recht, dir, allmächtiger Vater, zu danken und in den Heiligen deine Gnade zu rühmen."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Inmitten der Kirche berufst du Menschen, sich Christus zu weihen und mit ganzer Hingabe das Himmelreich zu suchen. In ihnen offenbarst du deinen Ratschluss, uns Menschen die ursprüngliche Heiligkeit neu zu schenken und uns schon jetzt mit Freude an den Gütern der kommenden Welt zu erfüllen durch unseren Herrn Jesus Christus."
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Durch ihn preisen dich Himmel und Erde, Engel und Menschen und singen wie aus einem Munde das Lob deiner Herrlichkeit:"
              }
            ]
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "communionAntiphon": {
    "options": [
      {
        "body": {
          "lines": {
            "la": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Quinque prudéntes vírgines accepérunt óleum in vasis suis cum lampádibus."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Média autem nocte clamor factus est: Ecce sponsus venit, exíte óbviam Christo Dómino"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "T. P."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "allelúia"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "es": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Las cinco vírgenes prudentes se llevaron alcuzas de aceite con las lámparas. A media noche se oyó una voz: «Que llega el esposo, salid al encuentro de Cristo, el Señor»"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "T. P."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Aleluya"
                }
              ]
            ],
            "en-US": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The five wise virgins brought flasks of oil with their lamps. Then at midnight, the cry went up: Behold, the Bridegroom is coming; come out to meet Christ the Lord"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "E. T."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "alleluia"
                }
              ]
            ],
            "pt-BR": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "As cinco virgens prudentes, ao tomarem suas lâmpadas, levaram óleo consigo."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Ouviu-se um grito na noite: Eis que chega o Esposo, ide ao encontro do Cristo!"
                }
              ]
            ],
            "it": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Le cinque vergini prudenti, insieme alle lampade, Cf. Mt 25, 4.6 presero con sé l’olio in piccoli vasi. A mezzanotte si levò un grido: «Ecco lo sposo!"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Andate incontro a Cristo Signore»"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "T. P."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "allelúia"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "fr": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Voici l’Époux qui vient !"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Sortez à la rencontre du Christ, le Seigneur"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "T. P."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "alléluia"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "de": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Die fünf klugen Jungfrauen nahmen außer den Lampen noch Öl in Krügen mit."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Mitten in der Nacht wurde laut gerufen: Der Bräutigam kommt! Geht Christus,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "dem Herrn, entgegen!"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "Österl. Zeit"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Halleluja"
                }
              ]
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "postcommunion": {
    "options": [
      {
        "body": {
          "lines": {
            "la": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Córporis et Sánguinis Unigéniti tui sacra percéptio, Dómine, ab ómnibus nos cadúcis rebus avértat, ut exémplo beátæ"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "valeámus tui et sincéra in terris caritáte profícere, et perpétua in cælis visióne gaudére. Per Christum."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "es": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Señor, que la santa comunión del Cuerpo y de la Sangre de tu Unigénito nos aparte de todas las cosas perecederas,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "para que, a ejemplo de santa"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ","
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "podamos servirte en la tierra con amor sincero y gozar eternamente de tu contemplación en el cielo."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Por Jesucristo, nuestro Señor."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "en-US": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "May the holy reception of the Body and Blood of your Only Begotten Son, O Lord, turn us away from the cares of this fleeting world, so that, following the example of blessed"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", we may grow in sincere love for you on earth and rejoice to behold you for eternity in heaven."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Through Christ our Lord."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "pt-BR": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Ó Pai, que a comunhão do Corpo e Sangue do vosso Filho nos desprenda das coisas perecíveis para que, a exemplo de santa"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ","
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "sempre mais vos amemos na terra e vos contemplemos eternamente no céu. Por Cristo, nosso Senhor."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "it": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "La comunione al Corpo e al Sangue del tuo unigenito Figlio ci liberi, o Padre,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "dagli affanni delle cose che passano, perché, sull’esempio di santa"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "progrediamo in terra nella vera carità e godiamo in cielo della tua visione senza fine. Per Cristo nostro Signore."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "fr": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "En participant au don que tu nous as fait,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Seigneur notre Dieu,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "nous avons renouvelé nos forces,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "et nous te supplions encore :"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "qu’à l’exemple de sainte"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ","
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "portant dans notre corps la mort de Jésus,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "nous cherchions à nous attacher à toi seul."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Par le Christ, notre Seigneur."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "de": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Ewiger Gott, der Empfang des Leibes und Blutes Christi lenke unseren Sinn von den vergänglichen Dingen auf das, was bleibt. Gib, dass wir nach dem Beispiel der heiligen"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "in aufrichtiger Liebe unsere Lebensaufgabe erfüllen und einst zur Anschauung deiner Herrlichkeit gelangen."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Darum bitten wir durch Christus, unseren Herrn."
                }
              ]
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
